OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F347A1783687767
OL,3,CDisturbing footage shows 'worst UK
OL,4,Cfootball violence in decades'
OL,6,FA warning, this footage contains
OL,7,Fscenes of extreme violence.
OL,9,FDisturbing footage showing Legia
OL,10,FWarsaw supporters clashing with West
OL,11,FMidlands Police in a night of violence
OL,12,Foutside Villa Park has been released
OL,13,Ffor the first time.
OL,15,FEight men have pleaded guilty to their
OL,16,Frole in the disorder on 30 November
OL,17,F2023, which was described as the
OL,18,F"worst UK football violence in
OL,19,Fdecades".
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/5
