PN,34702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F347A1783687767
OL,3,CDisturbing footage shows 'worst UK
OL,4,Cfootball violence in decades'
OL,6,FThree hundred West Midlands Police
OL,7,Fofficers and reinforcement from other
OL,8,Fforces faced a mob armed with
OL,9,Fdrainpipes, poles and branches for
OL,10,Faround thirty minutes.
OL,12,FSix officers were injured, including a
OL,13,FWest Mercia constable engulfed in
OL,14,Fflames when he was hit by a flare.
OL,16,FThe Polish football club fans can be
OL,17,Fseen throwing missiles and flares in
OL,18,Ffootage now released by the police.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,348,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F347A1783687767
OL,3,CDisturbing footage shows 'worst UK
OL,4,Cfootball violence in decades'
OL,6,FWest Midlands Police says two police
OL,7,Fdogs suffered injuries from broken
OL,8,Fglass, while a police horse was left
OL,9,Fwith cuts when a bottle was thrown at
OL,10,Fit.
OL,12,FAston Villa supporters were praised
OL,13,Ffor supporting officers.
OL,15,FDetective Inspector Tom Lyons, who led
OL,16,Fthe investigation, said: "This was
OL,17,Fhorrific violence from the so-called
OL,18,Ffans of Legia Warsaw, who threw
OL,19,Fmissiles at officers, attacked them
OL,20,Fand hurled abuse at them.
OL,26,@xD@ZOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/5
