OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,348,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F347A1783687767
OL,3,CDisturbing footage shows 'worst UK
OL,4,Cfootball violence in decades'
OL,6,F"Sadly it descended into some of the
OL,7,Fworst violence UK football has seen in
OL,8,Fdecades.
OL,10,F"But despite this, the officers on the
OL,11,Fnight displayed bravery and skilful
OL,12,Fteamwork to deliver a safe operation
OL,13,Fand protect the public."
OL,15,FEight men were due to stand trial at
OL,16,FBirmingham Crown Court for their
OL,17,Finvolvement in the violence.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOU
